{When WEST makes a Splinter bid, showing \H support and \C shortness, 
EAST naturally thinks about slam.

She uses RKCB 4NT, and WEST, with one Key Card and a \C Void, bids 6\C.

Just what EAST needed for the 6\H bid.}

