{This is the companion hand to Deal 18.

Again, EAST uses RKCB after the 4-4 \S fit is discovered. 
This time WEST shows two Key Cards without the \SQ.

Now EAST realizes that in addition to one outside Ace, there is a very possible loser 
in trumps. So she stops at 5\S.}

